## ABSOLUTELY FORBIDDEN

### Code & Architecture
- ❌ **any** in TypeScript — NEVER
- ❌ **inline styles** — use Tailwind classes only
- ❌ **magic numbers** — use named constants
- ❌ **code duplication** — DRY principle
- ❌ **functions > 50 lines** — split into smaller ones
- ❌ **files > 300 lines** — split into modules
- ❌ **nesting > 3 levels** — use early returns
- ❌ **console.log in production** — use proper logger
- ❌ **commented-out code** — delete it

### Security
- ❌ **secrets in code** — use env variables only
- ❌ **SQL without parameterization** — use Prisma / prepared statements
- ❌ **eval() and similar** — never
- ❌ **disabling CORS/CSRF** — without explicit approval

### Process
- ❌ **architecture changes without approval**
- ❌ **adding dependencies without justification**
- ❌ **deleting tests**
- ❌ **ignoring linter errors**

---

## ALWAYS DO

### Code
- ✅ **TypeScript strict mode** — all types explicit
- ✅ **Named exports** — no default exports
- ✅ **Input validation** — at all boundaries
- ✅ **Error handling** — try/catch with logging
- ✅ **Descriptive names** — variables describe their purpose

### Structure
- ✅ **One file — one responsibility**
- ✅ **Reusable components** — in shared/common
- ✅ **Constants in separate files**

### Documentation
- ✅ **JSDoc for public functions**
- ✅ **Comments for complex logic only**

---

## DECISION MAKING

### Autonomous decisions (do yourself)
- Variable/function naming
- Internal file structure
- Small refactoring (< 50 lines)
- Obvious bug fixes
- TypeScript type additions
- Code formatting

### Require approval (propose options)
- Project/module architecture
- Library and framework choices
- Folder structure changes
- DB schema changes
- Public API deletion/renaming
- Business logic changes

---

## NAMING STANDARDS

### Files
| Type | Format | Example |
|------|--------|---------|
| React components | PascalCase | `ProductCard.tsx` |
| Hooks | camelCase with use | `useProducts.ts` |
| Utilities | camelCase | `formatPrice.ts` |
| Types | camelCase.types | `product.types.ts` |
| Constants | camelCase.constants | `api.constants.ts` |

### Code
| Type | Format | Example |
|------|--------|---------|
| Variables | camelCase | `userName` |
| Functions | camelCase | `getProducts` |
| Classes | PascalCase | `ProductService` |
| Constants | UPPER_SNAKE | `API_BASE_URL` |
| Types/Interfaces | PascalCase | `ProductData` |

